      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BRING THE BEERS (1) comes off a moderate effort last start, finishing fourth at this track over 324m behind Greengrocer Tom (17.91). Good beginner assisted by the inside draw. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. BAD GIRL RIVER (5) continues to race well but is struggling to break through, placing at her last four runs. Last start finished 2nd over 324m at this track beaten 2.25 lengths (18.07) behind Zipping Popyrin in a Maiden on July 9. Good beginner but will need a little luck from a middle draw. Can feature again. QUEST FOR JUNIOR (3) has been hard to follow lately, running seventh (18.22) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at this track. Well placed here and should do much better. BLACK FELONESS (2) is in the mix despite finishing out of the placings here last start.",
